ot;i have 19 batwings and i keep killing bats but no more will drop&quot; He got really stressed so i gave him 5pp for 19, He said WOW Thats LOADS Of money thanx a lot, Anyway i buffed him up, then Went to Sol B to hunt and 15mins later i got a tell saying &quot;I have your other batwing&quot; See'ing as thought i didn't get a group i thought this was really nice of the guy so i went back and met him, We had a chat and he asked me a few questions then i saw he really was new,so i asked him to come with me to my bank and i'll see what i have spare. so i delved into the bank and gave him a full set of bronze (i know its crap but...) And a B.a.b.s It was a thrill to see someone excited. He ran around killing bats in one hit trying to get more batwings hehe. I keep the old crap that drops now-adays and give it to what i hope are true newbies. It earns it's own rewards :-)<br><br>My 2Cp<br><br>Kermus Treehuger<br>48th druid<br>Vanguards of Exellence<br>Merry Xmas <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/udrywit.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Drywit</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 92<br> <font color=#E9D756>(12/24/01 3:14:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2822.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My Christmas Experiment</span><hr size=1> Back when my Iksar SK was level 11 I was hunting Froglok Raiders in SoNH. A higher-level player was hanging out, I got my butt in a sling and he derailed the train that was after me.<br><br>Then he handed me a 2-Handed Practice sword.<br><br>I cut a swath through those froggies and made it my primary weapon up to about level 27.<br><br>On a trip through Innothule I gave it to a young, struggling Ogre SK.<br><br>That act of kindness inspired me to give aw